iv> </div> </div></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-section"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column" data-w="12" data-widget-type="cell" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1686645401556" style=""> <section class="heading-content" id="whyGreenwich"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <p style="font-weight: bold;" style="text-align: center;"><span>Boost your English speaking skills for success in Australia!</span></p> <div class="hs-video-widget" data-hsv-embed-id="2126c1d7-1451-4a1d-bbe4-ade85bf11d9a" data-hsv-status="loaded"> <div class="hs-video-container" style="max-width: 1920px; margin: 23px auto;"> <div class="hs-video-wrapper" style="position: relative; height: 0; padding-bottom: 56.25%"> <iframe allow="autoplay; fullscreen;" data-hsv-autoplay="false" data-hsv-full-width="false" data-hsv-height="1080" data-hsv-hidden-controls="false" data-hsv-id="158091302719" data-hsv-loop="false" data-hsv-muted="false" data-hsv-style="margin: 23px auto;" data-hsv-width="1920" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="origin" sandbox="allow-forms allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups" src="https://play.hubspotvideo.com/v/493380/id/158091302719?parentOrigin=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greenwichcollege.edu.au&amp;renderContext=hubl-iframe&amp;locale=en-au#hsvid=2126c1d7-1451-4a1d-bbe4-ade85bf11d9a" style="position: absolute !important; width: 100% !important; height: 100% !important; left: 0; top: 0; border: 0 none; pointer-events: initial" title="HubSpot Video"></iframe> </div> </div> </div> <p style="text-align: center;"><span>If you need a fast-track program to improve your spoken English and be easily understood, Pronunciation in Context is for you. This program focuses on English sounds, stress, and rhythm, enhancing your pronunciation for confident communication in everyday situations, whether it"s ordering food or acing a job interview.</span></p> </div> </div> </section></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1686645419705" style=""> <section class="gwcMoreSupport"> <div class="container"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span7 content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Who is this course for?</p> <p>Do you wonder if people can understand you? Are you having trouble understanding the people around you? Do you have difficulty with certain English sounds? Do you want to become a better communicator?</p> <p>This fun, interactive course has been designed for students who want to be more confident speaking and listening in English. </p> <p> </p> <p> </p> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1686645419705_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span5 image"> <img alt="couple3" class="txtimg" height="742" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 686px) 100vw, 686px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/05Hold_Images_New_Site/A-IMAGES/Couples/couple3.png?width=686&amp;height=742&amp;name=couple3.png" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.