cing skills you will need to survive and excel at university or college.</p> <p style="text-align: center;"> </p> </div> </div> </section></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-section"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_dnd_area-module-3" style=""> <section class="gwcMoreSupport"> <div class="container"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span7 content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Who is this course for?</p> <p>EAP is designed for upper intermediate-level English students who want to improve their academic English skills in preparation for further study at University or College in an English-speaking country.</p> <p>EAP provides a pathway to many Colleges and Universities in Australia</p> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_dnd_area-module-3_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span5 image"> <img alt="iStock-902440746-2" class="txtimg" height="837" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 1254px) 100vw, 1254px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-902440746-2.jpg?width=1254&amp;height=837&amp;name=iStock-902440746-2.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-902440746-2.jpg?width=627&amp;height=419&amp;name=iStock-902440746-2.jpg 627w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-902440746-2.jpg?width=1254&amp;height=837&amp;name=iStock-902440746-2.jpg 1254w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-902440746-2.jpg?width=1881&amp;height=1256&amp;name=iStock-902440746-2.jpg 1881w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-902440746-2.jpg?width=2508&amp;height=1674&amp;name=iStock-902440746-2.jpg 2508w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-902440746-2.jpg?width=3135&amp;height=2093&amp;name=iStock-902440746-2.jpg 3135w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-902440746-2.jpg?width=3762&amp;height=2511&amp;name=iStock-902440746-2.jpg 3762w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="1254"/> </div> </div> </div> </section> <div class="testimonial-modal modal" id="testimonial_modal"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <!-- Modal content--> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-body"> <div class="banner-video_pop"> <iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="390" src="" width="640"></iframe> </div> </div> <div class="modal-footer"> <button class="close">X</button> </div> </div> </div> </div></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-section"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_dnd_area-module-4" style=""> <section class="gwcMoreSupport"> <div class="container"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span6 content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000;">You will learn to</span></p> <ul> <li>Effectively participate in a university or college course</li> <li>Express facts, ideas and opinions in writing, using correct and appropriate vocabulary, grammatical structures for academic purposes</li> <li>Understand spoken English in conversations, discussions and lectures and take notes</li> <li>Speak clearly and confidently in English</li> <li>Write well-structured and formatted texts of various types - such as essays - and understand academic texts</li> <li>Understand and deliver seminar presentations in English in front of a group</li> <li>Apply the skills and language studied to the IELTS examination.</li> </ul> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_dnd_area-module-4_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span6 image"> <img alt="iStock-1384332902" class="txtimg" height="836" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 1254px) 100vw, 1254px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1384332902.jpg?width=1254&amp;height=836&amp;name=iStock-1384332902.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1384332902.jpg?width=627&amp;height=418&amp;name=iStock-1384332902.jpg 627w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1384332902.jpg?width=1254&amp;height=836&amp;name=iStock-1384332902.jpg 1254w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1384332902.jpg?width=1881&amp;height=1254&amp;name=iStock-1384332902.jpg 1881w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1384332902.jpg?width=2508&amp;height=1672&amp;name=iStock-1384332902.jpg 2508w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1384332902.jpg?width=3135&amp;height=2090&amp;name=iStock-1384332902.jpg 3135w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1384332902.jpg?width=3762&amp;height=2508&amp;name=iStock-1384332902.jpg 3762w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="1254"/> </div> </div> </div> </section> <div class="testimonial-modal modal" id="testimonial_modal"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <!-- Modal content--> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-body"> <div class="banner-video_pop"> <iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="390" src="" width="640"></iframe> </div> </div> <div class="modal-footer"> <button class="close">X</button> </div> </div> </div> 