g abilities and refining your command of the English language, enabling you to apply these skills effectively in a vocational education setting.</span></p> </div> </div> </section></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-section"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_dnd_area-module-3" style=""> <section class="gwcMoreSupport"> <div class="container"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span7 content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Who is this course for?</p> <p><span style="color: #000000;">English for Vocational Studies (EVS) is tailored for Upper Intermediate-level English students seeking an immersive academic English program for success in vocational studies.</span></p> <p><span style="color: #000000;">Upon completion, this course opens the door to certificate or diploma programs at leading Australian colleges. It also serves as a stepping stone to our English for Academic Purposes course, priming you for advanced studies at the university level.</span></p> <p><span style="color: #000000;">EVS is the ideal preparation for your upcoming vocational studies, providing a direct route to admission at Greenwich Hospitality, Health and Care, or Management College and other esteemed Australian vocational institutions.</span></p> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_dnd_area-module-3_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span5 image"> <img alt="iStock-1432589502-3" class="txtimg" height="836" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 1253px) 100vw, 1253px" 