iv> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Ongoing academic support</p> <p> <a class="cta_button pinkCTAsmall" href="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/english-courses/english-vocational-studies-evs?__hstc=122107220.8672ef33587d025b20e125db5f04f8fc.1761554828243.1761554828243.1761554828243.1&amp;__hssc=122107220.7.1761554828243&amp;__hsfp=3527509107&amp;hsutk=8672ef33587d025b20e125db5f04f8fc&amp;contentType=standard-page"> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy hover_section_part"> <div class="alignCenter"> <span class="hover-icon"><img alt="" size_type="" src=""/></span> </div> <p>Receive fortnightly one-on-one academic counselling so you know where to focus your efforts and can achieve greater success faster.</p> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1679629901131_" style=""></span> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-10 dnd-section"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column" data-w="12" data-widget-type="cell" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-11 dnd-row"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1681294655641" style=""> <div class="table-section"> <div class="container"