="heading-content" id="whyGreenwich"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> <img alt="Web_ST Star Awards 2024-RGB_Winner" height="193" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 380px) 100vw, 380px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=380&amp;height=193&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=190&amp;height=97&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 190w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=380&amp;height=193&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 380w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=570&amp;height=290&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 570w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=760&amp;height=386&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 760w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=950&amp;height=483&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 950w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=1140&amp;height=579&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 1140w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="380"/> </p> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Prepare for a successful business career</p> <p><span>Want to be job-ready as soon as you graduate? Learn high-level skills in marketing, customer service, team development, and project management - and build strong analytical and problem-solving skills to reach your career goals quickly.</span></p> </div> </div> </section></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1680705460735" style=""> <section class="gwcMoreSupport"> <div class="container"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span7 content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Who is this course for?</p> <p>The Certificate IV in Business is designed for students who want to start a successful career in Business in an English-speaking country.</p> <p>This course equips learners with sound business knowledge and extends their skills so that they can learn the basics of successfully contributing in a business. Students will learn to implement customer service strategies and basic leadership skills.</p> <p>Through our expert trainers and real-life case study approach, our graduates are job-ready faster. Our Studio+ programme offers students industry internship placement opportunities.</p> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1680705460735_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span5 image"> <img alt="iStock-915741300-2" class="txtimg" height="836" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 1254px) 100vw, 1254px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-915741300-2.jpg?width=1254&amp;height=836&amp;name=iStock-915741300-2.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-915741300-2.jpg?width=627&amp;height=418&amp;name=iStock-915741300-2.jpg 627w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-915741300-2.jpg?width=1254&amp;height=836&amp;name=iStock-915741300-2.jpg 1254w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-91574130