d row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_module_1720055451542" style=""> <section class="gwcMoreSupport"> <div class="container"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span6 content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Who is this course for?</p> <p>The Certificate IV in Leadership and Management is designed for students who want to build the skills and expertise to pursue leadership and management roles in business in an English-speaking country.</p> <p>This course helps students to develop skills across a range of areas including: customer service, financial administration and business communication to achieve success in a leadership position. Through our expert trainers and real-life case study approach, our graduates are job-ready faster.</p> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_module_1720055451542_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span6 image"> <img alt="iStock-1982627427" class="txtimg" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1982627427.jpg?width=2000&amp;name=iStock-1982627427.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1982627427.jpg?width=1000&amp;name=iStock-1982627427.jpg 1000w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1982627427.jpg?width=2000&amp;name=iStock-1982627427.jpg 2000w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1982627427.jpg?width=3000&amp;name=iStock-1982627427.jpg 3000w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iSto