ited for</p> <p>The Diploma of Leadership &amp; Management is for students who want to learn the skills and expertise required to achieve success in roles involving high-level management and leadership responsibilities.</p> <p>This course will take you to a new level in developing advanced aspects of leadership and management including how to plan, organise, implement and monitor the success of teams within an organisation. Perfect if you are fresh out of college or looking to fastrack and reboot your career path. You will learn key skills to apply in the workplace and accelerate your progress.</p> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_module_17200485698232_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span6 image"> <img alt="iStock-915741300" class="txtimg" height="836" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 1254px) 100vw, 1254px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-915741300.jpg?width=1254&amp;height=836&amp;name=iStock-915741300.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-915741300.jpg?width=627&amp;height=418&amp;name=iStock-915741300.jpg 627w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-915741300.jpg?width=1254&amp;height=836&amp;name=iStock-915741300.jpg 1254w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-915741300.jpg?width=1881&amp;height=1254&amp;name=iStock-915741300.jpg 1881w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-915741300.jpg?width=2508&amp;height=1672&amp;name=iStock-915741300.jpg 2508w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-915741300.jpg?width=3135&amp;height=2090&amp;name=iStock-915741300.jpg 3135w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-915741300.jpg?width=3762&amp;height=2508&amp;name=iStock-915741300.jpg 3762w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="1254"/> </div> </div> </div> </section> <div