fs/hubfs/Print_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-CMYK_Winner.jpg?width=1578&amp;height=800&amp;name=Print_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-CMYK_Winner.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Print_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-CMYK_Winner.jpg?width=789&amp;height=400&amp;name=Print_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-CMYK_Winner.jpg 789w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Print_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-CMYK_Winner.jpg?width=1578&amp;height=800&amp;name=Print_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-CMYK_Winner.jpg 1578w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Print_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-CMYK_Winner.jpg?width=2367&amp;height=1200&amp;name=Print_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-CMYK_Winner.jpg 2367w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Print_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-CMYK_Winner.jpg?width=3156&amp;height=1600&amp;name=Print_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-CMYK_Winner.jpg 3156w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Print_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-CMYK_Winner.jpg?width=3945&amp;height=2000&amp;name=Print_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-CMYK_Winner.jpg 3945w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Print_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-CMYK_Winner.jpg?width=4734&amp;height=2400&amp;name=Print_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-CMYK_Winner.jpg 4734w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="1578"/> </p> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Lead a project from start to finish</p> <p>Gain the knowledge and skills to effectively lead a project through from start to finish - including all aspects of a project from budget setting and tracking progress to managing development, controlling communication and managing human resources.</p> </div> </div> </section></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1686911807463" style=""> <section class="gwcMoreSupport"> <div class="container"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span7 content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Who is this course for?</p> <p>Diploma of Project Management is designed for people wanting to succeed in delivering projects across a number of industries in a variety of context such as leading new growth strategies, changing systems, restructuring teams or launching marketing events.</p> <p>Develop the knowledge and skills to effectively lead a project through from start to finish - including all aspects of a project from budget setting and tracking progress to managing development, controlling communication and managing human resources.</p> <p>Through our expert trainers and real-life case study approach, our graduates are job-ready faster.</p> <p>You will also have the opportunity to study for a globally recognised Project Management certification for FREE. Exclusive to Greenwich College students, save $1200 and join our <a href="/online-academy/capm-certification-preparation-course?hsLang=en-au" rel="noopener"><strong>Certified Associate in Project Management</strong></a> (CAPM) certification preparation course.</p> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1686911807463_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span5 image"> <img alt="iStock-1435087166" class="txtimg" height="782" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 1341px) 100vw, 1341px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1435087166.jpg?width=1341&amp;height=782&amp;name=iStock-1435087166.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1435087166.jpg?width=671&amp;height=391&amp;name=iStock-1435087166.jpg 671w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1435087166.jpg?width=1341&amp;height=782&amp;name=iStock-1435087166.jpg 1341w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1435087166.jpg?width=2012&amp;height=1173&amp;name=iStock-1435087166.jpg 2012w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1435087166.jpg?width=2682&amp;height=1564&amp;name=iStock-1435087166.jpg 2682w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1435087166.jpg?width=3353&amp;height=1955&amp;name=iStock-1435087166.jpg 3353w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1435087166.jpg?width=4023&amp;height=2346&amp;name=iStock-1435087166.jpg 4023w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="1341"/> </div> </div> </div> </section> <div class="testimonial-modal modal" id="testimonial_modal"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <!-- Modal content--> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-body"> <div class="banner-video_pop"> <iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="390" src="" width="640"></iframe> </div> </div> <div class="modal-footer"> <button class="close">X</button> </div> </div> </div> </div></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1686912296521" style=""> <section class="gwcMoreSupport"> <div class="container"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span6 content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">You will learn to</p> <span id="ginger-button-for-rephrase" style="left: 257px; top: 36px; position: fixed; z-index: 51; visibility: visible;" title="Rephrase"></span> <p><strong>BSBPMG530</strong> - Manage project scope (Core)<br/><strong>BSBPMG531</strong> - Manage project time (Core)<br/><strong>BSBPMG532</strong> - Manage project quality (Core)<br/><strong>BSBPMG533</strong> - Manage project cost (Core)<br/><strong>BSBPMG534</strong> - Manage project human resources (Core)<br/><strong>BSBPMG535</strong> - Manage project information and communication (Core)<br/><strong>BSBPMG536</strong> - Manage project risk (Core)<br/><strong>BSBPMG540</strong> - Manage project integration (Core)<br/><strong>BSBCMM511</strong> - Communicate with influence<br/><strong>BSBSTR502</strong> - Facilitate continuous improvement<br/><strong>BSBSUS511</strong> - Develop workplace policies and procedures for sustainability<br/><strong>BSBTWK502</strong> - Manage team effectiveness<br/><br/><strong>Career Opportunities:</strong><br/>Project Manager (generic), Project Manager (industry specific), Project Leader, Project Team Leader, Project Contract Manager and more.. </p> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1686912296521_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span6 image"> <img alt="Organisational Change Management" class="txtimg" height="628" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 876px) 100vw, 876px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Work%20Ready%20Backup/Work%20Ready%20Education%202021/Organisational%20Change%20Management.jpg?width=876&amp;height=628&amp;name=Organisational%20Change%20Management.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Work%20Ready%20Backup/Work%20Ready%20Education%202021/Organisational%20Change%20Management.jpg?width=438&amp;height=314&amp;name=Organisational%20Change%20Management.jpg 438w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Work%20Ready%20Backup/Work%20Ready%20Education%202021/Organisational%20Change%20Management.jpg?width=876&amp;height=628&amp;name=Organisational%20Change%20Management.jp