ntent" id="whyGreenwich"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> <img alt="Web_ST Star Awards 2024-RGB_Winner" height="193" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 380px) 100vw, 380px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=380&amp;height=193&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=190&amp;height=97&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 190w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=380&amp;height=193&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 380w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=570&amp;height=290&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 570w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=760&amp;height=386&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 760w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=950&amp;height=483&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 950w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=1140&amp;height=579&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 1140w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="380"/> </p> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Specialised content in digital and social media marketing is included in this qualification</p> <p>Do you want to become a savvy marketer? Learn the leading digital and social media tools and best practices used in modern business to succeed in the marketing communications industry - and gain expertise in communication, marketing concepts, media planning, social media and budgets.</p> </div> </div> </section></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1680775804761" style=""> <section class="gwcMoreSupport"> <div class="container"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span7 content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Who is this course for?</p> <p>The Diploma of Marketing and Communication is designed for students who want to become a savvy marketing and communications practitioner with digital and creative thinking skills in order to drive measurable marketing success.</p> <p>Learn the leading digital and social media tools and best practices used in modern business to succeed in the marketing communication industry and gain expertise in communication, marketing concepts, media planning and social media.</p> <p>Our course is designed with today digital world at the core of our syllabus. All learning concepts are delivered in a relevant digital context.</p> <p><strong>There is no direct entry into this course. Students are required to complete a Certificate IV in Marketing and Communication (BSB40820) as a pre-requisite.</strong></p> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1680775804761_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span5 image"> <img alt="iStock-842856832" class="txtimg" height="836" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 1254px) 100vw, 1254px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-842856832.jpg?width=1254&amp;height=836&amp;name=iStock-842856832.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iSt