t-weight: bold;">Lead and manage programs to successful completion</p> <p>Programs are large scale projects made up of several projects that are dependant on each other. Outlining objectives, planning execution, managing operations, and reporting on status are just a few of the functions involved in carrying out a successful program.Gain the knowledge and the skills to delegate projects appropriately and deliver programs that impact business growth.</p> </div> </div> </section></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1686908168205" style=""> <section class="gwcMoreSupport"> <div class="container"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span7 content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Who is this course for?</p> <p>Advanced Diploma of Program Management is best suited for people who have experience in a project management role and are seeking to enhance their program management skills to further their career.</p> <p>This course will provide students with a solid foundation in Program Management across a range of industry contexts. Individuals at this level use initiative and judgement to direct, plan and lead a range of program functions.</p> <p>A program is defined as a set of interrelated projects, each of which has a Project Manager. A â€˜programâ€™ of projects refers to a number of related projects managed by the same person.</p> <p>You will also have the opportunity to study for a globally recognised Project Management certification for <strong>FREE</strong>. Exclusive to Greenwich College students, save $1200 and join our <a href="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hubfs/2022/CAPM%20CERTIFICATION%20-%20PREP%20COURSE.pdf?hsLang=en-au" rel="noopener" target="_blank"><strong>Certified Associate in Project Management</strong></a> (CAPM) certification preparation course.</p> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1686908168205_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span5 image"> <img alt="iStock-1839176058-2" class="txtimg" height="482" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 725px) 100vw, 725px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1839176058-2.jpg?width=725&amp;height=482&amp;name=iStock-1839176058-2.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1839176058-2.jpg?width=363&amp;height=241&amp;name=iStock-1839176058-2.jpg 363w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1839176058-2.jpg?width=725&amp;height=482&amp;name=iStock-1839176058-2.jpg 725w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1839176058-2.jpg?width=1088&amp;height=723&amp;name=iStock-1839176058-2.jpg 1088w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1839176058-2.jpg?width=1450&amp;height=964&amp;name=iStock-1839176058-2.jpg 1450w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1839176058-2.jpg?width=1813&amp;height=1205&amp;name=iStock-1839176058-2.jpg 1813w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1839176058-2.jpg?width=2175&amp;height=1446&amp;name=iStock-1839176058-2.jpg 2175w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="725"/> </div> </div> </div> </section> <div class="testimonial-modal modal" id="testimonial_modal"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <!-- Modal content--> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-body"> <div class="banner-video_pop"> <iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="390" src="" width="640"></iframe> </div> </div> <div class="modal-footer"> <button class="clos