s-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_dnd_area-module-2" style=""> <section class="heading-content" id="whyGreenwich"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Become a next generation business leader</p> <p><span>The Advanced Diploma of Leadership and Management provides you with the knowledge and initiative to lead your company, your business or your team from the front, and guide them to success. You will learn pivotal attributes that will help you recruit, train, shape and manage your teams and colleagues all the way to the top of your field.</span></p> </div> </div> </section></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-section"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column" data-w="12" data-widget-type="cell" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1681179321642" style=""> <section class="gwcMoreSupport"> <div class="container"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span7 content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Who is this course for?</p> <p style="text-align: justify;">Advanced Diploma of Leadership and Management is designed for students looking to develop a senior management skill set and leadership attributes across a range of areas, including business administration and management, general administration and business communication. Students will learn leadership and management strategies and techniques to help them excel in the work place, including how to develop organisational strategies, how to create business development plans and how to lead and manage organisational change.<br/><br/>To enable an accelerated path to a chosen career, students will be at the cutting edge of human resources, company innovation and learn how to communicate with influence. <br/><br/><strong>There is no direct entry into this course. Students are required to complete a Diploma course with a BSB code as a pre-requisite.</strong><br/><br/><strong>Here are available Greenwich Management College BSB Diploma course options: </strong><br/><a href="/management-courses/diploma-business-digital-transformation?hsLang=en-au" rel="noopener"><strong>Diploma of Business | Digital Transformation (BSB50120)</strong></a><br/><a href="/management-courses/diploma-marketing-communication?hsLang=en-au" rel="noopener"><strong>Diploma of Marketing and Communication (BSB50620)</strong></a><br/><a href="/management-courses/diploma-of-leadership-management?hsLang=en-au" rel="noopener"><strong>Diploma of Leadership and Management (BSB50420)</strong></a><br/><a href="/management-courses/diploma-project-management?hsLang=en-au" rel="noopener"><strong>Diploma of Project Management (BSB50820)</strong></a></p> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1681179321642_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span5 image"> <img alt="iStock-902440746-2" class="txtimg" height="837" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 1254px) 100vw, 1254px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-902440746-2.jpg?width=1254&amp;height=837&amp;name=iStock-902440746-2.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-902440746-2.jpg?width=627&amp;height=419&amp;name=iStock-902440746-2.jpg 627w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-902440746-2.jpg?width=1254&amp;height=837&amp;name=iStock-902440746-2.jpg 1254w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-9024407