et" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_dnd_area-module-2" style=""> <section class="heading-content" id="whyGreenwich"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> <img alt="Web_ST Star Awards 2024-RGB_Winner" height="193" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 380px) 100vw, 380px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=380&amp;height=193&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=190&amp;height=97&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 190w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=380&amp;height=193&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 380w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=570&amp;height=290&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 570w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=760&amp;height=386&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 760w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=950&amp;height=483&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 950w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png?width=1140&amp;height=579&amp;name=Web_ST%20Star%20Awards%202024-RGB_Winner.png 1140w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="380"/> </p> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Transmit knowledge, skills, and ideas to others</p> <p>This is a Graduate Diploma of Management for the 21st century leader. Recent events are showing us that leaders and managers have to show an increasing ability to be flexible and adapt to challenges that constantly appear in our ever changing global world. Develop the skills to stay one step ahead and engage and inspire your teams</p> </div> </div> </section></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1686912598991" style=""> <section class="gwcMoreSupport"> <div class="container"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span7 content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Who is this course for?</p> <p>The Graduate Diploma of Management (Learning) is the perfect choice for those who wish to advance their knowledge and skills for professional or further learning. It develops and refines the relevant skills and knowledge to empower students to achieve success in roles involving management and leadership. Aspects of these are covered in a holistic manner, including</p> <ul> <li>Planning for and managing operational plans</li> <li>Managing workplace relationships</li> <li>Managing key HR functions</li> <li>Understanding and interpreting legislative requirements</li> <li>Sourcing and applying information</li> <li>Building and leading effective teams</li> <li>Engaging a wide range of stakeholders and coordinating promotional activities</li> </ul> <p> </p> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1686912598991_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span5 image"> <img alt="iStock-1305141042-Sep-27-2024-06-49-44-5404-AM" class="txtimg" height="836" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 1254px) 100vw, 1254px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1305141042-Sep-27-2024-06-49-44-5404-AM.jpg?width=1254&amp;height=836&amp;name=iStock-1305141042-Sep-27-2024-06-49-44-5404-AM.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1305141042-Sep-27-2024-06-49-44-5404-AM.jpg?width=627&amp;height=418&amp;name=iStock-1305141042-Sep-27-2024-06-49-44-5404-AM.jpg 627w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1305141042-Sep-27-2024-06-49-44-5404-AM.jpg?width=1254&amp;height=836&amp;name=iStock-1305141042-Sep-27-2024-06-49-44-5404-AM.jpg 1254w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1305141042-Sep-27-2024-06-49-44-5404-AM.jpg?width=1881&amp;height=1254&amp;name=iStock-1305141042-Sep-27-2024-06-49-44-5404-AM.jpg 1881w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1305141042-Sep-27-2024-06-49-44-5404-AM.jpg?width=2508&amp;height=1672&amp;name=iStock-1305141042-Sep-27-2024-06-49-44-5404-AM.jpg 2508w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1305141042-Sep-27-2024-06-49-44-5404-AM.jpg?width=3135&amp;height=2090&amp;name=iStock-1305141042-Sep-27-2024-06-49-44-5404-AM.jpg 3135w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1305141042-Sep-27-2024-06-49-44-5404-AM.jpg?width=3762&amp;height=2508&amp;name=iStock-1305141042-Sep-27-2024-06-49-44-5404-AM.jpg 3762w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="1254"/> </div> </div> </div> </section> <div class="testimonial-modal modal" id="testimonial_modal"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <!-- Modal content--> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-body"> <div class="banner-video_pop"> <iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="390" src="" width="640"></iframe> </div> </div> <div class="modal-footer"> <button class="close">X</button> </div> </div> </div> </div></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-typ