hubfs/05Hold_Images_New_Site/Courses/WhyGreenwichIMages/PracticalCaseStudies_360x430.jpg?width=900&amp;height=1075&amp;name=PracticalCaseStudies_360x430.jpg 900w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/05Hold_Images_New_Site/Courses/WhyGreenwichIMages/PracticalCaseStudies_360x430.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1290&amp;name=PracticalCaseStudies_360x430.jpg 1080w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="360"/> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Practical case studies to strengthen learning</p> <p> <a class="cta_button pinkCTAsmall" href="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/management-courses/graduate-diploma-management-course?__hstc=122107220.8672ef33587d025b20e125db5f04f8fc.1761554828243.1761554828243.1761554828243.1&amp;__hssc=122107220.19.1761554828243&amp;__hsfp=3527509107&amp;hsutk=8672ef33587d025b20e125db5f04f8fc&amp;contentType=standard-page"> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy hover_section_part"> <div class="alignCenter"> <span class="hover-icon"><img alt="" size_type="" src=""/></span> </div> <p>Greenwich Management Collegeâ€™s Diploma of Project Management features extensive use of real-life case studies to support learning, delivering valuable insights and applications to Australian business.</p> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1680493664749_" style=""></span> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/05Hold_Images_New_Site/Courses/WhyGreenwichIMages/FunInteractiveClassesOPTION2_360x430.jpg?width=360&amp;height=430&amp;name=FunInteractiveClassesOPTION2_360x430.jpg");"> <div class="row-