 only accredited Diploma of E-Commerce, designed to provide you with the essential skills needed in the online business world. This course covers a wide range of topics from creating and optimizing e-commerce platforms to developing digital marketing strategies and managing customer relationships.</p> </div> </div> </section></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1680775804761" style=""> <section class="gwcMoreSupport"> <div class="container"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span7 content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Who is this course for?</p> <p>- Aspiring E-commerce professionals: Those looking to start a career in the rapidly growing e-commerce industry.</p> <p>- Current business owners: Entrepreneurs and small business owners who want to expand their online presence and improve their digital business strategies.</p> <p>- Marketing and sales professionals: Individuals in marketing or sales roles who wish to enhance their e-commerce skills and knowledge.</p> <p>- Career changers: Professionals from other fields who are seeking to transition into the e-commerce sector.</p> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1680775804761_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span5 image"> <img alt="iStock-693275166" class="txtimg" height="815" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 1287px) 100vw, 1287px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-693275166.jpg?width=1287&amp;height=815&amp;name=iStock-693275166.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-693275166.jpg?width=644&amp;height=408&amp;name=iStock-693275166.jpg 644w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-693275166.jpg?width=1287&amp;height=815&amp;name=iStock-693275166.jpg 1287w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-693275166.jpg?width=1931&amp;height=1223&amp;name=iStock-693275166.jpg 1931w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-693275166.jpg?width=2574&amp;height=1630&amp;name=iStock-693275166.jpg 2574w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-693275166.jpg?width=3218&amp;height=2038&amp;name=iStock-693275166.jpg 3218w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-693275166.jpg?width=3861&amp;height=2445&amp;name=iStock-693275166.jpg 3861w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="1287"/> </div> </div> </div> </section> <div class="testimonial-modal modal" id="testimonial_modal"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <!-- Modal content--> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-body"> <div class="banner-video_pop"> <iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="390" src="" width="640"></iframe> </div> </div> <div class="modal-footer"> <button class="close">X</button> </div> </div> </div> </div></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1680776273563" style=""> <section class="gwcMoreSupport"> <div class="container"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span7 content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">You will learn to</p> <span id="ginger-button-for-rephrase" style="left: -68px; top: 36px; position: fixed; z-index: 51; visibility: visible;" title="Rephrase"></span> <p><strong>NAT11269001</strong> - Evaluate e-commerce models and operations<br/><strong>NAT11269002</strong> - Plan optimisation of the path to purchase in an e-commerce environment<br/><strong>NAT11269003</strong> - Create and publish product listings for e-commerce stores<br/><strong>NAT11269004</strong> - Implement and optimise the online post-purchase process<br/><strong>NAT11269005</strong> - Deliver and enhance customer service practices in an e-commerce environment<br/><strong>NAT11269006</strong> - Develop strategies to maximize performance of an e-commerce site<br/><strong>NAT11269007</strong> - Apply marketing automation to e-commerce customer communications<br/><strong>NAT11269008</strong> - Leverage social media and online communities for e-commerce growth<br/><strong>NAT11269009</strong> - Develop paid traffic strategies for online sales<br/><strong>NAT11269010</strong> - Develop plans to capitalise on emerging e-commerce opportunities</p> <p><strong>Career Opportunities: </strong>E-commerce Content Coordinator, E-commerce Specialist, Marketing Specialist, E-commerce Manager, Online Retail Coordinator, Customer Service Manager - Online Retail, Online Sales Manager, Founder / Entrepreneur.</p> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1680776273563_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span5 image"> <img alt="iStock-1338814824" class="txtimg" height="836" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 1254px) 100vw, 1254px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1338814824.jpg?width=1254&amp;height=836&amp;name=iStock-1338814824.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1338814824.jpg?width=627&amp;height=418&amp;name=iStock-1338814824.jpg 627w, https://www.greenwic