div class="span12 gwcContainer"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionHead"> <p style="font-weight: bold;" style="text-align: left;">Where will this course take me?</p> <div id="ginger-button-for-rephrase-container" style="left: -46px; top: -23px; position: fixed; z-index: 51; visibility: visible;"><span id="ginger-button-for-rephrase" style="position: relative;"></span> <div class="ginger-button-for-rephrase-tooltip">Rephrase with Ginger (Ctrl+Alt+E)</div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12"> <p>Our<strong> Diploma of Hospitality Management</strong> course provides the right qualifications that enhance studentsâ€™ industry knowledge while creating a pathway to work in any hospitality industry as a small business or departmental manager. Students will have the opportunity to work within a wider range of venues such as restaurants, hotels, clubs, pubs, catering, cafes, and coffee shops, as well as specializing in accommodation services, food and beverage.</p> <p><strong>Possible job titles the Diploma of Hospitality Management course can offer:</strong> Unit manager catering operations, Banquet or function manager, Executive housekeeper, Front office manager, Restaurant manager, Kitchen manager, Motel manager, Hotel Manager, Executive chef, Cafe manager, Club manager, Bar manager and Sous chef. </p> <section> <div><p style="text-align: center;"><strong>OUR PARTNERS</strong></p></div> <img alt="hospitality_hotel logos" height="417" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 1667px) 100vw, 1667px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/hospitality_hotel%20logos.png?width=1667&amp;height=417&amp;name=hospitality_hotel%20logos.png" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/hospitality_hotel%20logos.png?width=834&amp;height=209&amp;name=hospitality_hotel%20logos.png 834w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/hospitality_hotel%20logos.png?width=1667&amp;height=417&amp;name=hospitality_hotel%20logos.png