 class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich (1)" height="430" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(1).png?width=360&amp;height=430&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(1).png" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(1).png?width=180&amp;height=215&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(1).png 180w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(1).png?width=360&amp;height=430&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(1).png 360w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(1).png?width=540&amp;height=645&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(1).png 540w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(1).png?width=720&amp;height=860&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(1).png 720w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(1).png?width=900&amp;height=1075&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(1).png 900w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(1).png?width=1080&amp;height=1290&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(1).png 1080w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="360"/> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Guaranted Vocational Placement</p> <p class="read-more"> <a href=""> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy"> <p class="alignCenter"><span class="tick"> </span></p> <ul> <li> <p>We have dedicated vocational placement coordinators to organise students" desired work experience. We work with a variety of industry partners and provide complete assistance to students with resume preparation, interviews and matching their availability to suitable employers.</p> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20%282%29.png");"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich (2)" height="430" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(2).png?width=360&amp;height=430&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(2).png" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(2).png?width=180&amp;height=215&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(2).png 180w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(2).png?width=360&amp;height=430&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(2).png 360w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(2).png?width=540&amp;height=645&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(2).png 540w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(2).png?width=720&amp;height=860&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(2).png 720w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(2).png?width=900&amp;height=1075&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(2).png 900w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(2).png?width=1080&amp;height=1290&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(2).png 1080w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="360"/> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Real-life Practical Classes &amp; Facilities</p> <p class="read-more"> <a href=""> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy"> <p class="alignCenter"><span class="tick"> </span></p> <ul> <li> <p>We provide students with real-life kitchen experience in our practical classes. We ensure students will learn with real industry facilities, making them more confident in their first work place, all done through on-site practical training.</p> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20%286%29.png");"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich (6)" height="430" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(6).png?width=360&amp;height=430&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(6).png" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(6).png?width=180&amp;height=215&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(6).png 180w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(6).png?width=360&amp;height=430&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(6).png 360w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(6).png?width=540&amp;height=645&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(6).png 540w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(6).png?width=720&amp;height=860&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(6).png 720w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(6).png?width=900&amp;height=1075&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(6).png 900w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(6).png?width=1080&amp;height=1290&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(6).png 1080w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="360"/> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Learn From Industry Experts</p> <p class="read-more"> <a href=""> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy"> <p class="alignCenter"><span class="tick"> </span></p> <ul> <li> <p>Students will learn from expert professionals who have worked for years in the hospitality industry, These trainers bring a wide range of experience to the classroom and demonstrate how dynamic the hospitality industry is.</p> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20%284%29.png");"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich (4)" height="430" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(4).png?width=360&amp;height=430&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(4).png" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(4).png?width=180&amp;height=215&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(4).png 180w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(4).png?width=360&amp;height=430&amp;name=why-study-hospitality-with-Greenwich%20(4).png 360w, https://w