96a-5d5a-4bfc-9ff6-dd43e781209b.jpg 1158w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="386"/> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>CHCDIV001 </strong></p> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>Work with diverse people<span style="color: red;"> </span></strong></p> <p class="read-more"> <a href=""> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy"> <p class="alignCenter"><span class="tick"> </span></p> <ul> <li> <p>This unit relates to the skills and knowledge required to work respectfully with people from diverse social and cultural groups and</p> <p>situations, including Aboriginal and/or Torres Strait Islander people.</p> <p>This unit applies to all workers.</p> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1300745916-modified-3213d1b3-e6d2-4192-bbf7-bd600d09b8c0.jpg?width=1600&amp;height=2000&amp;name=iStock-1300745916-modified-3213d1b3-e6d2-4192-bbf7-bd600d09b8c0.jpg");"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="iStock-1300745916-modified-3213d1b3-e6d2-4192-bbf7-bd600d09b8c0" height="2000" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1300745916-modified-3213d1b3-e6d2-4192-bbf7-bd600d09b8c0.jpg?width=1600&amp;height=2000&amp;name=iStock-1300745916-modified-3213d1b3-e6d2-4192-bbf7-bd600d09b8c0.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1300745916-modified-3213d1b3-e6d2-4192-bbf7-bd600d09b8c0.jpg?width=800&amp;height=1000&amp;name=iStock-1300745916-modified-3213d1b3-e6d2-4192-bbf7-bd600d09b8c0.jpg 800w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1300745916-modified-3213d1b3-e6d2-4192-bbf7-bd