orkers across a range of community services contexts.</p> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg");"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398" height="483" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 386px) 100vw, 386px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg?width=193&amp;height=242&amp;name=iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg 193w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg 386w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg?width=579&amp;height=725&amp;name=iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg 579w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg?width=772&amp;height=966&amp;name=iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg 772w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg?width=965&amp;height=1208&amp;name=iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg 965w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg?width=1158&amp;height=1449&amp;name=iStock-1460177254-modified-36d0ede2-a535-473e-bcac-6851cdb55398.jpg 1158w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="386"/> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>HLTWHS002 </strong></p> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>Follow safe work practicesfor direct client care</strong></p> <p class="read-more"> <a href=""> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy"> <p class="alignCenter"><span class="tick"> </span></p> <ul> <li> <p>Concerns training on the skills and knowledge required for a worker to participate in safe work practices to ensure their own health and safety, and that of others in work environments that involve caring directly for clients. It has a focus on maintaining safety of the worker, the people being supported and other community members.</p> <p>This unit applies to all workers who require knowledge of workplace health and safety (WHS) to carry out their own work, in both centre-based and home-based service provision.</p> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg");"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c" height="483" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 386px) 100vw, 386px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg?width=193&amp;height=242&amp;name=iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg 193w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg 386w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg?width=579&amp;height=725&amp;name=iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg 579w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg?width=772&amp;height=966&amp;name=iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg 772w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg?width=965&amp;height=1208&amp;name=iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg 965w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg?width=1158&amp;height=1449&amp;name=iStock-1305053558-modified-9a3ced05-6479-4c26-99a5-891487e86c8c.jpg 1158w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="386"/> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>CHCPAL001</strong></p> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>Deliver care services using a palliative approach</strong></p> <p class="read-more"> <a href=""> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy"> <p class="alignCenter"><span class="tick"> </span></p> <ul> <li> <p>In this unit the learner is taught the performance outcomes, skills and knowledge required to provide care for people with life-limiting illness and those within the normal ageing process using a palliative approach.</p> <p>This unit applies to workers in a residential or community context. Work performed requires some discretion and judgement and is carried out under regular direct or indirect supervision.</p> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg?width=354&amp;height=443&amp;name=iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg");"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199" height="443" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 354px) 100vw, 354px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg?width=354&amp;height=443&amp;name=iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg?width=177&amp;height=222&amp;name=iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg 177w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg?width=354&amp;height=443&amp;name=iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg 354w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg?width=531&amp;height=665&amp;name=iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg 531w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg?width=708&amp;height=886&amp;name=iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg 708w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg?width=885&amp;height=1108&amp;name=iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg 885w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg?width=1062&amp;height=1329&amp;name=iStock-1644171048-modified-ad6a3627-c5c0-449c-abac-804361c93199.jpg 1062w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="354"/> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>CHCPRP001 </strong></p> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>Develop and maintain networks </strong><strong> </strong></p> <p class="read-more"> <a href=""> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy"> <p class="alignCenter"><span class="tick"> </span></p> <ul> <li> <p>Lessons learned from this unit refers to the skills and knowledge required to identify networking and collaboration needs and develop formal and informal partnerships to enhance service delivery and improve professional practice.</p> <p>This unit applies to work in all industry sectors, and to individuals who take pro-active responsibility for improving collaboration between workers and organisations.</p> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1487468070-modified-adbb8a5b-0697-4dd7-a863-195f6bc1fcf4.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1487468070-modified-adbb8a5b-0697-4dd7-a863-195f6bc1fcf4.jpg");"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="iStock-1487468070-modi