s="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>CHCAGE003 </strong></p> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>Coordinate services for older people</strong></p> <p class="read-more"> <a href=""> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy"> <p class="alignCenter"><span class="tick"> </span></p> <ul> <li> <p>This unit describes the skills and knowledge to provide services to an older person. It involves following and contributing to an<br/>established individual plan.</p> <p>This unit applies to workers in a residential or community context, or those in personal care or support services that work with older<br/>people. Work performed requires some discretion and judgement and is carried out under regular direct or indirect supervision.</p> <p> </p> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg");"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9" height="483" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 386px) 100vw, 386px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg?width=193&amp;height=242&amp;name=iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg 193w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg 386w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg?width=579&amp;height=725&amp;name=iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg 579w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg?width=772&amp;height=966&amp;name=iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg 772w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg?width=965&amp;height=1208&amp;name=iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg 965w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg?width=1158&amp;height=1449&amp;name=iStock-844452116-modified-448191cd-1213-43fa-a238-73b0245e5fa9.jpg 1158w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="386"/> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>CHCAGE001 </strong></p> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>Facilitate the empowerment of older people</strong></p> <p class="read-more"> <a href=""> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy"> <p class="alignCenter"><span class="tick"> </span></p> <ul> <li> <p>This unit describes the skills and knowledge required to respond to the goals and aspirations of older people and provide support<br/>services in a manner that focuses on improving health outcomes and quality of life, using a person-centred approach.</p> <p><br/>This unit applies to support workers in residential or community contexts.</p> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg");"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8" height="483" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 386px) 100vw, 386px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg?width=193&amp;height=242&amp;name=iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg 193w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg 386w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg?width=579&amp;height=725&amp;name=iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg 579w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg?width=772&amp;height=966&amp;name=iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg 772w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg?width=965&amp;height=1208&amp;name=iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg 965w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg?width=1158&amp;height=1449&amp;name=iStock-1575056447-modified-c219858a-99c0-442d-874f-82be2cf6c7e8.jpg 1158w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="386"/> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>CHCAGE004 </strong></p> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>Implement interventions with older people at risk</strong></p> <p class="read-more"> <a href=""> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy"> <p class="alignCenter"><span class="tick"> </span></p> <ul> <li> <p>This unit describes the skills and knowledge required to work in partnership with older people and their carers to implement<br/>interventions in the context of an individualised plan to reduce risk.</p> <p><br/>This unit applies to support workers in a residential or community context. Work performed requires a range of well developed skills where some discretion and judgement is required. Workers will take responsibility for their own outputs under direct or indirect<br/>supervision.</p> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg");"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee" height="483" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 386px) 100vw, 386px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg?width=193&amp;height=242&amp;name=iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg 193w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg 386w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg?width=579&amp;height=725&amp;name=iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg 579w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg?width=772&amp;height=966&amp;name=iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg 772w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg?width=965&amp;height=1208&amp;name=iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg 965w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg?width=1158&amp;height=1449&amp;name=iStock-1753755836-modified-c582c80e-fbf4-465d-bcf0-c905b42176ee.jpg 1158w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="386"/> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>CHCCCS023 </strong></p> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>Support independence and wellbeing</strong></p> <p class="read-more"> <a href=""> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy"> <p class="alignCenter"><span class="tick"> </span></p> <ul> <li> <p>Training on this unit encompasses the skills and knowledge required to provide individualised services in ways that support independence, as well as physical and emotional wellbeing.</p> <p><br/>This unit applies to workers in a range of community services contexts who provide frontline support services within the context of<br/>an established individualised plan.</p> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div> </div> </div> </main> <div data-global-resource-path="greenwich-theme-2023/templates/partials/footer.html"><div class="footer-section"> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_module_16789435566256" style=""><div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 gwcFooter"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionPaddingSmall alignCenter"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> Your success starts at Greenwich. </p> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 gwcFtrSitemap"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 gwcContainer"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span3"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> Locations </p> <p> </p><p><a href="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/your-campus/sydney?hsLang=en-au"><strong>Sydney Pitt St. Campus</strong></a><br/><span>Level 2, 396 Pitt Street</span><br/><span>Sydney NSW 2000 </span><br/><span>+61 2 9264 2223</span></p> <p></p> <p> </p><p><a href="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/your-campus/sydney-mary-st?hsLang=en-au"><strong>Sydney Mary St. Campus</strong></a><br/><span>Level 2, 72 Mary Street</span><br/><span>Sydney NSW 2000 </span><br/><span>+61 2 8317 0502</span></p> <p></p> <p> <a href="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/your-campus/melbourne?hsLang=en-au"><strong>Melbourne Campus</strong></a><br/><span>Level 8, 120 Spen