/id/155192524645?parentOrigin=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greenwichcollege.edu.au&amp;renderContext=hubl-iframe&amp;locale=en-au#hsvid=15839c34-1504-43d5-afdb-97f09cc9e6a9" style="position: absolute !important; width: 100% !important; height: 100% !important; left: 0; top: 0; border: 0 none; pointer-events: initial" title="HubSpot Video"></iframe> </div> </div> </div> <p> </p> </div> </div> </section></div> </div><!--end widget-span --> </div><!--end row--> </div><!--end row-wrapper --> <div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" data-w="12" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" style=""> <div class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1685698025050" style=""> <section class="gwcMoreSupport"> <div class="container"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span7 content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> </p> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Who is this course for?</p> <p>The Diploma of Community Services (Case Management) is designed for individuals who are interested in pursuing a career in community services with a focus on case management.</p> <p> This course is suitable for those who wish to work in roles that involve providing support, guidance, and tailored assistance to individuals and communities in need.</p> <p> If you have a passion for making a positive impact, empowering others, and playing a key role in the well-being of the community, this course is tailored to help you build the necessary skills and knowledge for a rewarding career in the field of community services.</p> <p> </p> <div class="hs-cta-node"> <span class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_cta" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="cta" id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1685698025050_" style=""></span> </div> </div> <div class="span5 image"> <img al