c="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1300317789-modified-d4a32b91-aa6e-4a78-9bd2-7c440b851c78.jpg?width=382&amp;height=477&amp;name=iStock-1300317789-modified-d4a32b91-aa6e-4a78-9bd2-7c440b851c78.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1300317789-modified-d4a32b91-aa6e-4a78-9bd2-7c440b851c78.jpg?width=191&amp;height=239&amp;name=iStock-1300317789-modified-d4a32b91-aa6e-4a78-9bd2-7c440b851c78.jpg 191w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1300317789-modified-d4a32b91-aa6e-4a78-9bd2-7c440b851c78.jpg?width=382&amp;height=477&amp;name=iStock-1300317789-modified-d4a32b91-aa6e-4a78-9bd2-7c440b851c78.jpg 382w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1300317789-modified-d4a32b91-aa6e-4a78-9bd2-7c440b851c78.jpg?width=573&amp;height=716&amp;name=iStock-1300317789-modified-d4a32b91-aa6e-4a78-9bd2-7c440b851c78.jpg 573w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1300317789-modified-d4a32b91-aa6e-4a78-9bd2-7c440b851c78.jpg?width=764&amp;height=954&amp;name=iStock-1300317789-modified-d4a32b91-aa6e-4a78-9bd2-7c440b851c78.jpg 764w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1300317789-modified-d4a32b91-aa6e-4a78-9bd2-7c440b851c78.jpg?width=955&amp;height=1193&amp;name=iStock-1300317789-modified-d4a32b91-aa6e-4a78-9bd2-7c440b851c78.jpg 955w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1300317789-modified-d4a32b91-aa6e-4a78-9bd2-7c440b851c78.jpg?width=1146&amp;height=1431&amp;name=iStock-1300317789-modified-d4a32b91-aa6e-4a78-9bd2-7c440b851c78.jpg 1146w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="382"/> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>CHCLEG003 Manage legal and ethical compliance</strong></p> <p class="read-more"> <a href=""> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy"> <p class="alignCenter"><span class="tick"> </span></p> <ul> <li> Focuses on the skills and knowledge required to research information about compliance and ethical practice responsibilities, and<br/>then develop and monitor policies and procedures to meet those responsibilities.<br/>This unit applies to people working in roles with managerial responsibility for legal and ethical compliance in small to medium sized<br/>organisations. There may or may not be a team of workers involved. </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg?width=399&amp;height=500&amp;name=iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg");"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411" height="500" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 399px) 100vw, 399px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg?width=399&amp;height=500&amp;name=iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg?width=200&amp;height=250&amp;name=iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg 200w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg?width=399&amp;height=500&amp;name=iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg 399w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg?width=599&amp;height=750&amp;name=iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg 599w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg?width=798&amp;height=1000&amp;name=iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg 798w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg?width=998&amp;height=1250&amp;name=iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg 998w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg?width=1197&amp;height=1500&amp;name=iStock-1473162531-modified-1c071e24-4663-4473-b96e-e91c9779c411.jpg 1197w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="399"/> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>CHCDIV001 Work with diverse people</strong></p> <p class="read-more"> <a href=""> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy"> <p class="alignCenter"><span class="tick"> </span></p> <ul> <li> Covers the skills and knowledge required to work respectfully with people from diverse social and cultural groups and situations,<br/>including Aboriginal and/or Torres Strait Islander people. This unit applies to all workers. </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1132630713.jpg?width=724&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1132630713.jpg");"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="iStock-1132630713" height="483" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 724px) 100vw, 724px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1132630713.jpg?width=724&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1132630713.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1132630713.jpg?width=362&amp;height=242&amp;name=iStock-1132630713.jpg 362w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1132630713.jpg?width=724&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1132630713.jpg 724w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1132630713.jpg?width=1086&amp;height=725&amp;name=iStock-1132630713.jpg 1086w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1132630713.jpg?width=1448&amp;height=966&amp;name=iStock-1132630713.jpg 1448w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1132630713.jpg?width=1810&amp;height=1208&amp;name=iStock-1132630713.jpg 1810w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1132630713.jpg?width=2172&amp;height=1449&amp;name=iStock-1132630713.jpg 2172w" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" width="724"/> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frontCopy"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>CHCDIV002 Promote Aboriginal and/or Torres Strait Islander cultural safety</strong></p> <p class="read-more"> <a href=""> Read More </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 bck2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 sectionCopy"> <p class="alignCenter"><span class="tick"> </span></p> <ul> <li> Entails the skills and knowledge required to identify Aboriginal and/or Torres Strait Islander cultural safety issues in the workplace,<br/>model cultural safety in own work practice, and develop strategies to enhance cultural safety.<br/>This unit applies to people working in a broad range of roles including those involved in direct client service, program planning,<br/>development and evaluation contexts. </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1368361279-modified-94a3d0c7-7ba8-430a-9915-6f72f25544c6.jpg?width=382&amp;height=479&amp;name=iStock-1368361279-modified-94a3d0c7-7ba8-430a-9915