actice through a process of reflection and ongoing<br/>professional development.<br/>This unit applies to workers in all industry sectors who take pro-active responsibility for their own professional development. </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1405341643-modified-5722baa7-3a92-48c3-9d0f-782ec3c3a979.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1405341643-modified-5722baa7-3a92-48c3-9d0f-782ec3c3a979.jpg");"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="iStock-1405341643-modified-5722baa7-3a92-48c3-9d0f-782ec3c3a979" height="483" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 386px) 100vw, 386px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1405341643-modified-5722baa7-3a92-48c3-9d0f-782ec3c3a979.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1405341643-modified-5722baa7-3a92-48c3-9d0f-782ec3c3a979.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1405341643-modified-5722baa7-3a92-48c3-9d0f-782ec3c3a979.jpg?width=193&amp;height=242&amp;name=iStock-1405341643-modified-5722baa7-3a92-48c3-9d0f-782ec3c3a979.jpg 193w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1405341643-modified-5722baa7-3a92-48c3-9d0f-782ec3c3a979.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1405341643-modified-5722baa7-3a92-48c3-9d0f-782ec3c3a979.jpg 386w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1405341643-modified-5722baa7-3a92-48c3-9d0f-782ec3c3a979.jpg?width=579&amp;height=725&amp;name=iStock-1405341643-modified-5722baa7-3a92-48c3-9d0f-782ec3c3a979.jpg 579w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1405341643-modified-5722baa7-3a92-48c3-9d0f-782ec3c3a979.jpg?width=772&amp;height=966&amp;name=iStock-1405341643-modified-5722baa7-3a92-48c3-9d0f-782ec3c3a979.jpg 772w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1405341643-modifie