ge to take a leadership role in the delivery of quality case management.<br/>This includes disseminating information and providing advice on practice issues relating to case management within the<br/>organisation. Workers at this level provide supervision to others according to organisational policies and procedures. </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="span4 featureContentWrap2"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frnt2" style="background-image: url("https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1591340539-modified-0519c009-1dfc-450b-9d2c-d0760d371dd3.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1591340539-modified-0519c009-1dfc-450b-9d2c-d0760d371dd3.jpg");"> <div class="row-fluid"> <div class="span12 frntImg"> <img alt="iStock-1591340539-modified-0519c009-1dfc-450b-9d2c-d0760d371dd3" height="483" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 386px) 100vw, 386px" src="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1591340539-modified-0519c009-1dfc-450b-9d2c-d0760d371dd3.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1591340539-modified-0519c009-1dfc-450b-9d2c-d0760d371dd3.jpg" srcset="https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1591340539-modified-0519c009-1dfc-450b-9d2c-d0760d371dd3.jpg?width=193&amp;height=242&amp;name=iStock-1591340539-modified-0519c009-1dfc-450b-9d2c-d0760d371dd3.jpg 193w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1591340539-modified-0519c009-1dfc-450b-9d2c-d0760d371dd3.jpg?width=386&amp;height=483&amp;name=iStock-1591340539-modified-0519c009-1dfc-450b-9d2c-d0760d371dd3.jpg 386w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1591340539-modified-0519c009-1dfc-450b-9d2c-d0760d371dd3.jpg?width=579&amp;height=725&amp;name=iStock-1591340539-modified-0519c009-1dfc-450b-9d2c-d0760d371dd3.jpg 579w, https://www.greenwichcollege.edu.au/hs-fs/hubfs/iStock-1591340539-modified-0519c009-1dfc-450b-9d2c-d0760d371dd3.jpg?width=772&amp;height=966&amp;name=iStock-1591340539-modified-0519c009-1dfc-